room_title: Escape room "Drago's Castle" by 5 Wits Arlington in Arlington (VA)
room_description: A mighty and terrifying dragon has broken out of the storybook world and is roaming free in the castle. You’ll need to team up with a princess to navigate the castle’s corridors, break free of the dungeon, and find the book with the power to seal the beast back in its pages. The princess will be a powerful ally on your quest, but take care – if she uses too much of her magic helping you, that won’t spell a storybook ending when it comes time to face the dragon!
